        <item>
            <title>【CES 2024】LG Signature OLED T 电视	透明屏幕抢眼 + 极强科幻感</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:17:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lg]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Signature OLED T]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1213776</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>除了宣布与 Google 合作的新闻外，LG 发布会最瞩目的肯定是全无线设计兼拥有透明荧幕的 LG Signature OLED T 电视首度真身亮相。Edward 就在发布会为大家近距离拍到它的外貌，现在就与大家分享一下这款既富艺术感亦有极强科幻感的全新旗舰电视吧。</p><h2>全透明荧幕不破坏家居设计</h2><p>LG 最新推出的 Signature OLED T，最特别之处肯定是它的 77 吋全透明设计的 4K OLED 面板。传统智能电视始终有硬件、背板等，所以挂在客厅墙上，始终会破坏整体家居设计氛围。而 LG 今次推出的 Signature OLED T，就采用全透明荧幕设计，配以极幼的荧幕边框，令它即使放在窗前，用家也可以穿透电视荧幕看到背后的窗外风景，同时间采用透明玻璃的电视荧幕仍会显示内容，在艺术感上它不会破坏整体家居设计氛围（当然它始终仍有边框及仍可颇明显看到荧幕玻璃，未做到完全隐形，但已比传统电视好得多），而透明玻璃同时为用家带来资讯及电视后的风景也让用家犹如置身科幻感极强的空间内，笔者现场肉眼所见，观感确实十分震撼。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LG 发布会的重磅消息，肯定是这部全新无线电视 Signature OLED T 的发布啦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲它最特别之处肯定是 77 吋的全透明 4K OLED 荧幕，笔者现场所见真的可以透过面板清晰看到电视背后的景物，十分厉害。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加上电视透框依然十分幼，所以它的「隐形度」相比传统电视确实高很多。不过 LG 方面表示这设计仍非最终定案，外框仍然在开发中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而且不只是电视荧幕关上时，即使启动后在显示内容，仍可透过透明荧幕看到背后风景，艺术感及科幻感均十分强。</p><h2>睇片时可将荧幕变非透明</h2><p>可能大家会问：如此「通透」，万一浏览影片时岂非对画面有所影响？LG 亦有想到这一点，用家只需要在睇片时将透明模式关闭，就可令荧幕变成非透明，就不会对欣赏影片有所影响了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当然，透明荧幕在播放影片时始终对画质有一定影响，尤其是背后风景如果是较光亮。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲所以它的「透明模式」是可以关闭的，关上后浏览观感就与一般 4K OLED 电视分别不大。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而显示相比影片较静态的画面时，透明模式确实可为用家带来十分震撼的视觉效果。</p><h2>仍采全无线设计 + 极幼边框</h2><p>至于电视设计上，大致上与去年 CES 大展现身过的 M 系无线电视差不多，主机板及各种接驳端子仍然保留在另设的「小盒子」上，画面就会透过无线方式传输到电视上播放。官方亦有表示这次看到的外型不一定是最终成品，它的外壳仍然在开发中，而推出日期及售价亦未定，不过应该最快也要年底，也应该是「天价」品吧。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Signature OLED T 仍然采用类似 M 系无线电视的设计，所以主机板、端子等仍然设于这个「小盒子」内，并以无线模式传输影像到电视播放。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/14/steam-deck-oled-review/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Steam Deck OLED 电脑游戏掌机，荧幕超亮丽 + 续航、游戏效能有惊喜</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/steam-deck-hk/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Steam Deck OLED 2023 香港开箱评测，效能，荧幕，续航力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/lg-announce-coop-with-google/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】LG 宣布与 Google 合作	2024 起 OLED TV 将预载支援 Chromecast 及 Google Home</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up/wireless-home/audio-visual/">【CES 2024】LG Signature OLED T 电视	透明屏幕抢眼 + 极强科幻感</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
