        <item>
            <title>【开箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 SUPER 显示卡　抢先看 Founder Edition 真身</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 00:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nvidia RTX]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 40 SUPER]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 4070 SUPER]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1213633</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NVIDIA GeForce RTX 40 SUPER 系列正式在 CES 2024 消费电子产品展览发布。全新产品线包括有 GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER、GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER 和 GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER。SUPER 系列带来了效能提升，除了为游戏带来更流畅体验之外，也为 AI 应用提供更强的处理能力。公版 GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 今日就新鲜热辣来到了 unwire 编辑部，就等小编同大家先开箱看看这张新卡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08772-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08772-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08772.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08775-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08775-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08775.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08748-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08748-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08748.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08744-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08744-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08744.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08776-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08776-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08776.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07973-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07973-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07973.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 RTX 4070 SUPER 同样使用到最新电源转换线供电，需要连接两条 PCI-e 电源线</p><p>我们将在日后提供更详细评测、跑分测试结果给大家参考。今次就先同大家开箱。从相片中可看到，GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 公版卡卡身用上黑色金属外壳，外壳大小与早前推出的 RTX 4070、RTX 4060Ti 没有看得出的分别。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08762-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08762-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08762.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以公版卡来说 RTX 4070（上）、RTX 4070 SUPER（下） 体积大致相同</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08766-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08766-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08766.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ RTX 4070（后方）、RTX 4070 SUPER（前方） 体积大致相同</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08757-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08757-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08757.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三张显示卡厚度比对</p><p>而同 RTX 4090、RTX 4080 比较，本卡的体积明显更为细小，更适合细机箱用户选购。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213644" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08760-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08760-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08760-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲将历代公版卡作一个比较 (4060 Ti 乃非公版)，可看到体积、长度大致分为两种，而今次的 RTX 4070 SUPER 卡身就几乎同 RTX 4070, RTX 4060 Ti 相同</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08761-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08761-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08761.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲单纯比较 RTX 4090（上）与 RTX 4070 SUPER（下）的卡面面积分别</p><p>NVIDIA 一次过为 RTX 4080、RTX 4070 Ti 同 RTX 4070 都作一个全面升级。这三款显示卡可说是中阶、中高阶入门之选，在非 SUPER 版推出时因为各种因素，包括售价、供应，未能完全令游戏用家受落。今次推出 SUPER 版本，三个型号都有效能提升。重点是 SUPER 版效能提升，但价钱保持不变，今次开箱的 GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 的售价为 US$599（约港币 HK$4,677），美金价与当初 RTX 4070 推出时相同。</p><p>最新三款 RTX 40 SUPER 系列售价：</p><p>GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER US$999 起（约港币 HK$7,799）</p><p>1 月 31 日起发售</p><p>GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER US$799 起（约港币 HK$6,238）</p><p>1 月 24 日起发售</p><p>GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER US$599 起（约港币 HK$4,677）</p><p>1 月 17 日起发售</p><p>再睇睇 RTX 4070 SUPER 卡身更多细节：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08743-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08743-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08743.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08753-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08753-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08753.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08755-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08755-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08755-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08756-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08756-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08756.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲公版卡提供 1 个 HDMI 插口与 3 个 DisplayPort 插口</p><p>今次 NVIDIA 为最新的 SUPER 系列分割了 3 个不同的客户群。用户可按需要购入适合自己的显示卡。</p><h2>GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER：4G 游戏怪兽</h2><p>NVIDIA 形容 GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER 非常适合在 4K 解像度流畅地享受游戏。本卡内置基于 NVIDIA Ada Lovelace 架构的图像处理器，提供最高 52 Shader-TFLOP/s、121 RT TLOPS 以及 836 AI TOPS 的性能。</p><h2>GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER：中阶用家顶尖之选</h2><p>用于想选购中阶卡的用户来说，GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER 可以在 1440p 画质下提供极高流畅度，也支援 4K 的游戏体验。相对于 RTX 4070 Ti，它内置有更多 CUDA 核心，扩增到 16GB 的帧缓冲区和 256 位元的记忆体汇流排，记忆体频宽提升至 672GB/s。它的效能比起 RTX 3070 Ti 快 1.6 倍，在 DLSS 3 的加成下更可达 2.5 倍。</p><h2>GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER：更好的平衡</h2><p>今次 RTX 4070 SUPER 比起 RTX 4070 多出 20% 核心，相信将会是极高性价比的新产品（请留意我们不久后推出的评测文章）。NVIDIA 指它比起 RTX 3090 更快、功耗更低；在 DLSS 3 的加成下，更是有 1.5 倍的效能。显示卡同样支援深度学习超级采样 DLSS，以 AI 人工智能驱动，在游戏中生成画格与重建光线，结合光线追踪，提供更流畅的游戏体验。</p><p>详细测试报告及规格，会在日后再为大家送上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08746-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08746-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08746.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07971-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07971-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07971-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER 和 4070 SUPER，NVIDIA 创始版设计将直接通过 NVIDIA.com 和选定零售商提供。包括原厂时脉和超频版在内的自订板卡，适用于所有 GeForce RTX 40 SUPER 系列 GPU，将由供应商如 ASUS、Colorful、Gainward、GALAX、GIGABYTE、INNO3D、KFA2、MSI、Palit、PNY 和 ZOTAC 提供。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/lg-announce-coop-with-google/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】LG 宣布与 Google 合作	2024 起 OLED TV 将预载支援 Chromecast 及 Google Home</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/08/ces-2024-lg-projector-and-gaming-monitor/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】LG 细小投影机 + 电竞萤幕   4K UHD 镭射投影 + 240Hz 0.03 ms 曲面 OLED</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/08/ces-2024-evie-ring/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】EVIE 智能戒指，追踪身体数据 + 记录月经</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/">【开箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 SUPER 显示卡　抢先看 Founder Edition 真身</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
